milestones.description: Sri Lanka's 86 is the lowest score in ODIs. They broke the earlier record of 136
de Silva and Kaluperuma's 28-run partnership is the highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 21 between Bob Massie and Jeff Hammond
Deryck Murray has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for WI, going past Deryck Murray's 1
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for WI, going past Garry Sobers's 1
Keith Boyce has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for WI, going past Foster
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for most catches in an innings (3) in ODIs for WI, going past Rohan Kanhai's 1
Deryck Murray has broken the record for most dismissals (5) in ODIs for WI, going past David Murray's 1
Julien has become the top wicket-taker for WI in ODIs with 7 wickets, going past Holder's 3
Deryck Murray and Fredericks's 52-run partnership is WI's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 43 between Fredericks and Ron Headley
